Interface PersistedEntity

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Domain, Node, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EntityRelationship<T,S>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPersistedEntity, ActivityEntity, EventEntity, WbsEntity

    public interface PersistedEntity
extends java.io.Serializable, Node
    Interface for entity classes. The interface ensures that there will be an id attribute for an entity.
